 <H1>Strawman Definitions</H1> 
 <P><UL>
<LI><H2>Event notification service
</H2>
<UL>
<LI>No globally consistent definition or shared model
</UL></UL><UL>
<LI><H2>Notifications
</H2>
<UL>
<LI>Events, once observed at sources, generate  notifications, which are then delivered to sinks 
</UL></UL><UL>
<LI><H2>Notification messaging
</H2>
<UL>
<LI>Need an application-layer analogue to datagrams
</UL></UL><UL>
<LI><H2>Notification management mechanisms
</H2>
<UL>
<LI>Mailing list subscriptions, newsgroup creation, multicast address allocation, publish-and-subscribe, chat spanning tree construction, event coalescing</UL></UL></P>
